<div class="dash-content item-offer-overview">
	<div class="brown-heading-banner">Donate items</div>
	
	<%= image_tag('donate-initial/Lucy.png') %>

	<p class='info'>
		Instead of selling, throwing away, or storing unused items and supplies, post your surplus items on our item-offer board. Animal organizations will log in, search the board, and request the items they need. As a donor, you have complete control over who receives your donation. Organizations can also post their individual wishlists, which you can browse and then match your items directly.
		<hr/>
		By choosing an option below, you can begin helping animal organizations, while removing unneeded items from your home.
	</p>

	<div class='options'>
		<%= link_to "POST ITEM-OFFER", donor_new_item_offer_path, :class => 'post-item-offer' %>
		<%= link_to "FULFILL A WISHLIST",browse_wishlists_path, :class => 'fulfill-wishlist' %>
	</div>

	<%# TODO: refactor this later (for v2) %>
	<div class="content-box">
		<p class="big bold">Groups</p>
		
		<p class="small bold inline">Items</p>
		<p class="small inline">
		: Donate surplus inventory, overstock items, etc.; anything that could benefit an animal
		organization - you'll be surprised what it takes to run a shelter or rescue!
		</p>
		
		<br/>
		<br/>
		
		<p class="small bold inline">Other ways to give</p>
		<p class="small inline">
		: How about sponsoring a volunteer event? Hosting an adoption event in
		your facility? There are so many ways to get involved!
		</p>
		
		<br/>
		<br/>
		
		<p class="big bold">Individuals</p>
		
		<p class="small inline">
		Donate new/gently-used collars, leashes, laundry detergent, pet food, litter, and much,
		much more! Also visit the TIME section above to donate your time as a volunteer.
		</p>
		
		<br/>
		<br/>
		
		<p class="big bold">What do animal organizations need most?</p>
		
		<p class="small inline">
		If you're unsure whether an organization can benefit from your item, post an item-offer to
		the item-offer board and see who responds; you might be surprised! Alternatively, search
		wishlists by item category to see if an organization has already requested the item you'd like
		to donate.
		</p>
		
		<br/>
		<br/>
		
		<p class="big bold">Post an Item-offer. It's simple!</p>
		
		<p class="small inline">
		Step 1: Register or sign-in to your donor account.<br/>
		Step 2: Write your post title, description, and upload a photo of the item.<br/>
		Step 3: Post your item-offer!<br/>
		<br/>
		Your item-offer will be viewed by all of the animal organizations that are searching the site.<br/>
		To update or modify your item-offer post, login to your account at any time.<br/>
		</p>	
	</div>
</div>